# AI governance

Before non-trivial changes, pick the right specialist:

| Task | Invoke |
| ---- | ------ |
| Nuxt / SSR / routing / Nitro | `@nuxt-expert` |
| Vue components / reactivity | `@vuejs-expert` |
| UI / layout / visual polish | `@gem-designer` |
| Bugs / regressions | `@gem-debugger` |
| Performance / Web Vitals | `@frontend-performance-investigator` |
| Large feature scope | `@implementation-plan` |
| PR / commits | `@create-pr` or `@resume-pr` |

Global skills in `~/.agents/skills/` (vue-best-practices, nuxt4-patterns, web-design-guidelines) apply here too.

**Golden rule:** read surrounding code before adding new abstractions; prefer the smallest correct diff.
